concept.title: Upload test results to manually from Katalon Studio

conbody.p: You can also upload test results manually by following these steps:

li.p: Open Katalon Studio and go to the project you are working on.
Go to Test Suites or Test Suite Collection and choose your test suite.

image.alt: upload manually from ks to testops

li.p: Click on the Katalon TestOps tab at the top right corner and select Upload.
Choose the Team and Project you want to upload test results to.

conbody.p: You have uploaded test results manually to Katalon TestOps from Katalon Studio.
